==Charts==
{{Wikipedia books|A Girl like Me}}
In 2009, "A Girl Like Me" debuted and peaked on the [[Productores de M<U+00FA>sica de Espa<U+00F1>a|Spanish Singles Chart]] at number 38 on November 29, 2009, over three and a half years after the release of the album.<ref name="SpanishCharts">{{cite web|url=http://spanishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Rihanna&titel=A+Million+Miles+Away&cat=s|title=Rihanna - A Million Miles Away|publisher=[[Productores de M<U+00FA>sica de Espa<U+00F1>a]]|accessdate=2011-10-15}}</ref> 
